# E-Commerce Backend API

## Project Overview

This project is a RESTful E-Commerce Backend API built using Flask and SQLAlchemy. It provides secure JWT authentication, role-based authorization, product and category management, shopping cart functionality, order processing, and an admin dashboard. The project follows a modular architecture and includes automated testing with Pytest and interactive API documentation using Swagger (Flasgger).

## Features

- User Registration & Login
- JWT Authentication
- Role-Based Authorization (Admin & Customer)
- Product Management (CRUD)
- Category Management (CRUD)
- Shopping Cart
- Checkout & Order Management
- Admin Dashboard
- Swagger API Documentation
- Pytest Test Suite
- 87% Test Coverage

## Technologies Used

- Python 3.11
- Flask
- Flask-SQLAlchemy
- Flask-Migrate
- SQLite
- JWT (PyJWT)
- Flasgger (Swagger UI)
- Pytest
- Git & GitHub

